no.ovitas.compass2.model.knowledgebase
Class RelationTypeSetting

java.lang.Object
  no.ovitas.compass2.model.knowledgebase.RelationTypeSetting

public class RelationTypeSetting
extends Object

This class represents a relation type settings, that can be used for configuring a relation type within a knowledge base.

Author:
Csaba Daniel
